WEBVTT

01:32.100 --> 01:34.940
[How dare you!?]

01:35.020 --> 01:38.030
[Episode 28]

02:20.790 --> 02:23.030
I—your new Emperor—am standing here
before you.

02:23.030 --> 02:24.160
Why do you not kneel?

02:24.630 --> 02:25.190
Kneel!

02:26.190 --> 02:30.520
Long live Your Majesty!

03:25.310 --> 03:26.110
Who is there?

03:26.430 --> 03:26.870
Who?

03:27.560 --> 03:29.100
I am the Emperor.

03:29.400 --> 03:31.680
Who dares to laugh at me?

03:32.190 --> 03:34.390
You're nothing but a lowborn bastard—

03:35.800 --> 03:37.400
the child of a lowly maid.

03:38.150 --> 03:40.750
And you think you're worthy of
calling me Mother?

03:40.750 --> 03:41.610
You're only fit

03:42.190 --> 03:44.390
to be trampled underfoot by Xiahou Dan!

03:44.870 --> 03:45.400
Beat him.

03:45.910 --> 03:46.950
Beat him hard!

03:58.400 --> 03:58.840
Bo!

03:59.870 --> 04:00.360
Bo!

04:01.150 --> 04:01.590
Bo!

04:01.910 --> 04:02.360
Bo!

04:02.710 --> 04:03.150
Bo.

04:03.800 --> 04:04.630
My poor Bo.

04:05.150 --> 04:06.080
Are you alright?

04:08.190 --> 04:09.460
The child is innocent.

04:10.430 --> 04:12.630
I beg you, please let Bo go.

04:13.430 --> 04:14.280
It's my fault.

04:14.630 --> 04:15.780
It's all my fault.

04:16.920 --> 04:18.050
Let him know

04:18.680 --> 04:20.070
who truly calls the shots

04:20.070 --> 04:21.339
in Great Xia!

04:22.120 --> 04:22.620
No!

04:23.680 --> 04:25.430
Weren't you asking to be beaten?

04:25.430 --> 04:26.560
Don't hit her!

04:27.030 --> 04:27.590
Mother!

04:28.240 --> 04:29.000
Mother!

04:30.680 --> 04:31.270
Mother!

05:34.490 --> 05:38.550
[Peiyang]

05:38.670 --> 05:38.970
You.

05:39.120 --> 05:41.190
Those men are wearing
the border army's armor.

05:41.190 --> 05:41.720
It seems

05:42.000 --> 05:44.040
they've taken full control of
Peiyang City.

05:44.040 --> 05:44.510
Show yours.

05:44.510 --> 05:45.480
But if they've occupied the city,

05:45.480 --> 05:46.950
-You may go.
-why would they reopen the gates

05:46.950 --> 05:48.360
and allow the common people come and go?

05:48.360 --> 05:49.830
His Majesty said in his letter

05:49.830 --> 05:52.090
that he left reinforcements in Peiyang.

05:52.190 --> 05:53.480
We must enter the city at once...

05:53.480 --> 05:54.210
Turn around.

05:54.360 --> 05:55.159
And find them.

05:56.070 --> 05:57.830
Only then will we have a chance
to rescue His Majesty.

05:57.830 --> 05:59.830
But the border army has
tens of thousands of troops.

05:59.830 --> 06:01.670
If we enter now and get exposed,

06:02.070 --> 06:03.750
there will truly be no escape for us.

06:03.750 --> 06:05.120
-Nothing ventured,
-You, come here.

06:05.120 --> 06:06.050
nothing gained.

06:07.240 --> 06:09.100
This is our only option right now.

06:09.640 --> 06:11.040
It seems these guards...

06:11.190 --> 06:11.480
You may enter.

06:11.480 --> 06:12.800
Are only checking luggage.

06:12.800 --> 06:13.130
Go on.

06:13.520 --> 06:15.680
They don't seem to be looking for anyone.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.310
Your Highness,

06:16.310 --> 06:17.370
it's still unwise.

06:17.680 --> 06:19.480
Did His Majesty leave any token?

06:19.600 --> 06:21.120
How about letting us enter the city
to search first?

06:21.120 --> 06:24.780
We'll come back to fetch Your Highness
once the news is confirmed.

06:25.390 --> 06:26.190
Token...

06:26.630 --> 06:27.140
Yours.

06:27.750 --> 06:28.410
Move along.

06:35.390 --> 06:37.720
Thank you for bringing us all the way
to Peiyang.

06:37.720 --> 06:39.920
I've had them prepare some travel expenses
for you.

06:39.920 --> 06:40.780
Your Highness.

06:42.980 --> 06:45.120
There's no need for you
to follow us any further.

06:45.120 --> 06:46.650
Find a place to settle down.

06:49.600 --> 06:50.130
Let's go.

06:51.070 --> 06:53.310
There's no reason for you guys
to risk your lives for me.

06:53.310 --> 06:55.040
Let's enter the city together.

07:01.640 --> 07:05.680
[Peiyang]

07:02.360 --> 07:02.690
Go on.

07:04.860 --> 07:05.660
You may enter.

07:06.630 --> 07:07.190
Let's go.

07:08.240 --> 07:08.770
Go ahead.

07:09.630 --> 07:10.490
You. Come here.

07:11.360 --> 07:12.680
-Stop.
-What's inside?

07:12.680 --> 07:13.140
Hold on.

07:20.330 --> 07:20.930
Come here.

07:20.950 --> 07:21.480
Officer.

07:22.480 --> 07:24.000
-We're here for medical treatment.
-Go on in.

07:24.000 --> 07:25.040
Take out your things for inspection.

07:25.040 --> 07:26.410
Follow me, all of you.

07:35.970 --> 07:39.390
[Prefect's Mansion]

07:42.170 --> 07:44.950
[Prefect's Mansion]

07:52.600 --> 07:54.130
General Lin, they're here.

07:57.630 --> 07:58.120
Wanyin.

07:58.800 --> 07:59.360
Bai?

08:05.240 --> 08:06.100
Smells so good!

08:06.200 --> 08:07.800
Put out another set of tableware,
will you?

08:07.800 --> 08:08.680
Don't be stingy.

08:08.680 --> 08:09.510
You are the Emperor now.

08:09.510 --> 08:11.370
What's one more set of tableware?

08:11.600 --> 08:13.510
Last night when I observed the stars,

08:13.510 --> 08:14.680
I noticed that the five stars
were about to align.

08:14.680 --> 08:15.250
So?

08:15.750 --> 08:16.750
Don't take this lightly.

08:16.750 --> 08:18.360
Master's divinations are always accurate,

08:18.360 --> 08:20.720
and he asked me to pass along
one more thing:

08:20.720 --> 08:22.190
your meeting with each other

08:22.190 --> 08:23.920
may not be a blessing after all.

08:27.950 --> 08:28.410
It's me.

08:32.710 --> 08:33.640
Come in, please.

08:38.179 --> 08:39.390
Moving around the camp,

08:39.390 --> 08:41.789
men's clothing is indeed more convenient.

08:41.960 --> 08:43.909
Here's the freshly brewed medicine.

08:43.909 --> 08:45.110
It's cooled down now.

08:48.030 --> 08:49.360
Thank you, General Lin.

08:59.120 --> 08:59.720
Actually,

09:01.320 --> 09:02.980
I still prefer you call me Bai.

09:03.430 --> 09:04.830
So who are you really, Bai

09:05.510 --> 09:06.440
or Lin Xuanying?

09:07.030 --> 09:08.030
I'm Lin Xuanying.

09:12.750 --> 09:15.030
I originally thought
you killed Lin Xuanying

09:15.030 --> 09:16.630
and were impersonating him.

09:17.360 --> 09:19.090
But after thinking it through,

09:19.670 --> 09:21.530
even though you've grown a beard,

09:21.870 --> 09:23.470
how could there be two people

09:23.600 --> 09:25.800
who look exactly the same in this world?

09:26.420 --> 09:28.350
I was born with a lock of white hair.

09:28.720 --> 09:29.240
Bai

09:30.360 --> 09:32.090
is the nickname Master gave me.

09:32.150 --> 09:34.000
But you had just finished
your apprenticeship.

09:34.000 --> 09:36.360
How did you become
a Deputy General so quickly?

09:36.360 --> 09:36.960
Well...

09:41.870 --> 09:45.000
Because you hadn't just finished
your apprenticeship.

09:50.870 --> 09:51.870
Our first meeting

09:53.000 --> 09:56.080
wasn't actually your first meeting
with His Majesty, was it?

09:56.080 --> 09:57.750
How long have you two known each other?

09:57.750 --> 09:59.280
This involves some secrets

10:00.790 --> 10:02.630
I can't speak of.

10:05.840 --> 10:07.100
If you are referring to

10:08.270 --> 10:10.470
His Majesty's past from another world,

10:13.750 --> 10:14.910
he wrote me a letter

10:16.070 --> 10:17.400
and told me everything.

10:22.480 --> 10:24.480
He tried every way to keep it from you

10:24.870 --> 10:26.870
because he was worried
it would scare you away.

10:26.870 --> 10:27.520
Years ago,

10:28.200 --> 10:30.670
my master, the Nameless,
cast a heavenly divination

10:30.670 --> 10:31.730
and predicted that

10:32.240 --> 10:34.500
the arrival of a child from another world

10:34.600 --> 10:36.330
would change the state's fate.

10:37.690 --> 10:40.120
He had intended to personally
step in to assist,

10:40.120 --> 10:41.250
but that divination

10:41.730 --> 10:43.530
revealed the workings of heaven

10:43.840 --> 10:45.700
and severely drained his energy.

10:45.840 --> 10:47.970
He could only stay home to recuperate,

10:48.510 --> 10:51.510
so he sent me out after graduating
to find His Majesty.

10:51.600 --> 10:53.460
But after I arrived at the palace,

10:53.790 --> 10:54.720
His Majesty said

10:55.750 --> 10:57.390
he had another purpose for me to serve.

10:57.390 --> 10:59.190
I've secretly trained a group of

10:59.240 --> 11:00.700
secret guards loyal to me.

11:01.600 --> 11:03.840
There's not much point in you
staying by my side to protect me.

11:03.840 --> 11:05.170
What do you need me to do?

11:09.120 --> 11:11.650
Without military power,
I have no trump card.

11:12.440 --> 11:13.840
No matter how I maneuver,

11:14.960 --> 11:17.290
I can't overthrow
my enemies in the court.

11:18.240 --> 11:18.790
So,

11:21.790 --> 11:24.050
have you thought about joining the army?

11:24.480 --> 11:26.810
After that, I infiltrated the Right Army.

11:27.910 --> 11:28.410
Indeed.

11:30.200 --> 11:31.000
The Right Army

11:31.630 --> 11:34.230
is the furthest from
Prince Duan's influence.

11:35.270 --> 11:37.120
Your small maneuvers in there

11:37.360 --> 11:38.690
would be hard to detect.

11:39.030 --> 11:40.720
It was also thanks to the fact that

11:40.720 --> 11:41.690
General You

11:42.080 --> 11:42.840
is a fool.

11:43.000 --> 11:44.910
As the commander of the Right Army,

11:44.910 --> 11:46.510
General You doesn't have a shred of
a true general's bearing.

11:46.510 --> 11:48.320
I don't expect him
to accomplish anything significant.

11:48.320 --> 11:49.720
But with him in that post,

11:50.270 --> 11:51.400
I can't command him,

11:51.790 --> 11:52.920
nor can Prince Duan.

11:53.660 --> 11:55.750
His Majesty and I worked,
one in the open and one in the shadows,

11:55.750 --> 11:57.570
so we could undermine him
right under the noses

11:57.570 --> 11:58.700
of all the factions.

11:59.150 --> 12:00.210
Now, the Right Army

12:00.950 --> 12:02.610
basically follows my orders.

12:04.790 --> 12:05.650
Your Highness.

12:06.480 --> 12:07.620
You can trust me.

12:07.990 --> 12:09.250
I gave you that hairpin

12:10.270 --> 12:11.800
for you to wear in your hair,

12:13.930 --> 12:15.190
not to hold in your hand

12:16.950 --> 12:18.610
as a weapon for self-defense.

12:27.630 --> 12:28.230
I'm sorry,

12:28.670 --> 12:29.110
Bai.

12:29.720 --> 12:31.650
So much has happened along the way,

12:32.720 --> 12:34.150
and meeting you in Peiyang

12:34.150 --> 12:35.150
was just too easy,

12:35.550 --> 12:36.670
so I couldn't help but be suspicious.

12:36.670 --> 12:37.470
I understand.

12:37.910 --> 12:39.750
That's why, starting from Peiyang,

12:39.750 --> 12:41.010
I've had my trusted men

12:41.530 --> 12:42.720
take shifts at the city gates
day and night,

12:42.720 --> 12:44.120
patrolling constantly.

12:44.120 --> 12:45.600
I was worried
you might disguise yourself,

12:45.600 --> 12:47.130
so I specifically told them

12:47.390 --> 12:49.720
to look out for a skylark-shaped hairpin.

12:51.000 --> 12:51.630
Thank you,

12:52.240 --> 12:52.600
Bai.

13:07.270 --> 13:08.030
Drag him

13:09.150 --> 13:10.540
away.

13:11.320 --> 13:12.390
Your Highness, please spare my life!

13:12.390 --> 13:14.190
Your Highness, please spare me!

13:14.750 --> 13:15.790
Your Highness, please spare me!

13:15.790 --> 13:16.600
Your Highness!

13:16.600 --> 13:17.800
Please spare my life!

13:25.670 --> 13:27.200
Imperial Physician Zhang,

13:28.720 --> 13:29.790
how is

13:31.030 --> 13:32.150
my leg?

13:36.150 --> 13:38.390
Your Highness is blessed with
extraordinary fortune.

13:38.390 --> 13:39.130
Given time,

13:39.790 --> 13:40.550
it'll surely heal...

13:40.550 --> 13:41.800
I want the truth!

13:42.720 --> 13:45.640
We will do our utmost to treat it.

13:45.720 --> 13:47.980
-We will do our best.
-We will do our best.

13:48.200 --> 13:49.060
Your Highness,

13:49.390 --> 13:50.520
the wound on your leg

13:50.670 --> 13:52.130
is highly prone to causing

13:52.200 --> 13:53.030
sepsis.

13:54.240 --> 13:55.950
Amputation is needed immediately

13:55.950 --> 13:57.200
to save your life.

14:02.320 --> 14:03.150
Very well.

14:05.760 --> 14:07.180
None of you could tell!

14:09.670 --> 14:10.270
Guards.

14:12.360 --> 14:13.480
Except for him,

14:14.270 --> 14:15.330
drag the rest away.

14:15.960 --> 14:17.320
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness! Your Highness!

14:17.320 --> 14:18.440
-Your Highness, please wait.
-Your Highness!

14:18.440 --> 14:20.300
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness.

14:20.360 --> 14:20.720
Your Highness,

14:20.720 --> 14:23.120
they simply didn't dare
tell you the truth.

14:26.440 --> 14:28.160
A bunch of useless trash.

14:29.510 --> 14:30.830
Get lost.

14:31.450 --> 14:33.090
-Thank you, Your Highness.
-Thank you, Your Highness.

14:33.090 --> 14:36.150
-Thank you, Your Highness.
-Thank you, Your Highness.

14:45.440 --> 14:46.080
What is

14:47.670 --> 14:48.670
your name?

14:50.390 --> 14:51.030
I am

14:52.080 --> 14:52.880
Xiao Tiancai.

14:54.590 --> 14:55.450
Your Highness,

14:55.600 --> 14:56.550
he is that Physician Xiao

14:56.550 --> 14:59.210
who has been
keeping the Empress Dowager alive.

15:05.720 --> 15:07.960
You said you could treat my leg.

15:08.720 --> 15:09.790
As I said,

15:11.550 --> 15:13.010
amputation is the only way

15:13.600 --> 15:14.790
to save your life.

15:15.750 --> 15:17.510
Are you absolutely certain?

15:19.320 --> 15:21.050
Even the greatest doctor alive

15:21.600 --> 15:23.720
wouldn't dare guarantee
absolute certainty.

15:23.720 --> 15:24.780
But as a physician,

15:25.360 --> 15:27.360
I'll surely give it my utmost effort

15:27.670 --> 15:28.530
to heal the sick

15:28.550 --> 15:29.410
and save lives.

15:33.480 --> 15:34.240
Alright.

15:35.600 --> 15:36.800
You may leave for now.

15:38.200 --> 15:39.670
I'll think about it.

15:43.440 --> 15:45.960
In fact, as early as
the beginning of last year,

15:45.960 --> 15:47.760
we were already fully prepared.

15:47.870 --> 15:48.480
We planned

15:48.960 --> 15:50.150
to purge the entire Right Army

15:50.150 --> 15:51.350
and then declare war.

15:52.320 --> 15:54.450
Although victory wasn't guaranteed,

15:54.910 --> 15:57.390
by striking unexpectedly
and catching them off guard,

15:57.390 --> 15:58.250
even if we died,

15:59.000 --> 16:02.460
we could take the Empress Dowager
and Prince Duan down with us.

16:03.910 --> 16:05.270
Those were His Majesty's exact words.

16:05.270 --> 16:06.150
But just then,

16:08.150 --> 16:08.950
you appeared.

16:13.720 --> 16:14.910
What's the point of laying out
such a grand scheme

16:14.910 --> 16:16.460
and taking so many detours?

16:16.670 --> 16:18.040
If we weren't going to attack directly,

16:18.040 --> 16:19.750
why send me to the Right Army
in the first place?

16:19.750 --> 16:20.750
Careful planning

16:22.910 --> 16:24.670
is to minimize casualties.

16:25.360 --> 16:27.320
But the situation is changing rapidly.

16:27.320 --> 16:28.790
If we keep dragging this out,

16:28.790 --> 16:31.520
even our last chance of victory
might evaporate.

16:32.000 --> 16:33.200
I just don't understand—

16:33.200 --> 16:35.000
why should you listen to a woman?

16:35.000 --> 16:36.130
Because in her eyes,

16:37.270 --> 16:39.200
whether it's peddlers and porters

16:39.390 --> 16:40.920
or commoners and peasants—

16:41.270 --> 16:42.270
every single life

16:43.910 --> 16:44.870
is precious.

16:47.840 --> 16:48.930
So that day,

16:48.960 --> 16:49.910
in the woods, you...

16:49.910 --> 16:50.240
Yes.

16:50.870 --> 16:51.930
I just wanted to see

16:52.720 --> 16:53.870
what kind of woman

16:54.960 --> 16:56.960
could actually change His Majesty.

17:06.750 --> 17:08.020
So in your eyes,

17:08.480 --> 17:10.540
I'm nothing more than a tiny skylark.

17:11.030 --> 17:12.069
I misjudged you.

17:13.589 --> 17:14.920
But His Majesty didn't.

17:14.920 --> 17:17.180
The world isn't just for roaming freely.

17:18.240 --> 17:19.700
She has her own ambitions.

17:20.400 --> 17:22.000
You only see her as a little bird

17:22.000 --> 17:23.400
that needs to be set free,

17:23.680 --> 17:24.680
but you fail to see

17:26.240 --> 17:27.839
how upright and noble she is—

17:28.920 --> 17:29.980
radiant as the sun,

17:30.790 --> 17:32.650
able to light up the vast blue sky.

17:36.310 --> 17:37.000
By the way,

17:38.030 --> 17:39.760
do you have news of His Majesty?

17:40.020 --> 17:41.080
We had agreed that

17:42.000 --> 17:43.480
if he managed to escape alive,

17:43.480 --> 17:45.080
we'd rendezvous in Peiyang.

17:45.150 --> 17:47.240
So I hurried here to
take control of the place,

17:47.240 --> 17:48.570
just to wait for you two.

17:48.920 --> 17:49.310
But

17:50.960 --> 17:51.960
only you arrived.

17:52.440 --> 17:53.460
What about Prince Duan?

17:53.460 --> 17:54.460
Is there any news?

17:54.720 --> 17:56.070
That scoundrel Prince Duan

17:56.070 --> 17:57.720
claims His Majesty was suddenly
struck with a serious illness

17:57.720 --> 17:59.070
and is recuperating inside the palace,

17:59.070 --> 18:00.790
but whether it's true or not is unknown.

18:00.790 --> 18:02.120
Is the source reliable?

18:03.540 --> 18:05.590
The capital is sealed tight right now.

18:05.590 --> 18:06.320
My spies will

18:06.960 --> 18:07.820
need more time.

18:12.960 --> 18:13.200
Then...

18:13.200 --> 18:14.060
Your Highness.

18:14.160 --> 18:15.220
It's getting late.

18:16.350 --> 18:17.750
You should get some rest.

18:21.110 --> 18:22.160
I will go and settle

18:22.160 --> 18:23.960
the people you brought with you.

18:24.920 --> 18:26.200
Early tomorrow morning,

18:26.200 --> 18:27.860
I'll show you something nice.

18:29.240 --> 18:30.100
I take my leave.

18:38.960 --> 18:39.620
Xiahou Dan.

18:40.440 --> 18:42.240
I've found the reinforcements.

18:44.350 --> 18:47.810
If you've truly been placed
under house arrest by Prince Duan,

18:50.270 --> 18:50.930
wait for me.

18:53.160 --> 18:55.020
I'll definitely come to save you.

19:00.550 --> 19:01.210
Gentlemen.

19:01.550 --> 19:02.920
We've endured humiliation for so long

19:02.920 --> 19:04.380
and finally gained power,

19:04.550 --> 19:07.030
so why are you sighing?

19:07.110 --> 19:07.990
Gained power?

19:08.590 --> 19:09.790
Throughout history,

19:10.070 --> 19:11.410
have you ever seen

19:11.440 --> 19:13.520
an emperor sitting in a wheelchair?

19:14.030 --> 19:16.090
So His Highness's leg can't be saved?

19:17.070 --> 19:18.350
Don't ask.

19:18.400 --> 19:20.720
With the Empress Dowager
being assassinated and the Crown Prince

19:20.720 --> 19:23.270
rebelling on one side, and the Emperor
gravely injured and the Empress in exile

19:23.270 --> 19:25.480
on the other—
after such chaos in the court,

19:25.480 --> 19:27.740
what's the point of holding court at all?

19:27.750 --> 19:29.070
We nearly lost our lives

19:29.070 --> 19:30.900
on Mount Bei.

19:31.830 --> 19:34.240
What a mess
the Imperial Observatory has made.

19:34.240 --> 19:35.880
They claimed it was an auspicious place,

19:35.880 --> 19:36.790
but in my opinion,

19:36.790 --> 19:38.370
it was complete nonsense.

19:42.790 --> 19:43.550
This is bad.

19:43.550 --> 19:44.610
This is really bad.

19:45.030 --> 19:46.000
Prince Duan has surrounded
His Majesty's chambers

19:46.000 --> 19:47.070
as tight as a drum.

19:47.350 --> 19:48.200
I asked around everywhere

19:48.200 --> 19:49.970
but couldn't get
the slightest bit of news.

19:49.970 --> 19:50.430
This...

19:50.720 --> 19:52.000
We must not lose our composure.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.720
If His Majesty had been killed,

19:53.720 --> 19:56.000
Prince Duan would have brought out
the Crown Prince to act as regent.

19:56.000 --> 19:57.420
There would be no need to
make such a commotion.

19:57.420 --> 19:58.720
With traitors and rebels in power,

19:58.720 --> 20:00.720
how can we sit idly by and do nothing?

20:02.070 --> 20:04.200
Even if we have to risk our lives today,

20:04.270 --> 20:05.670
we must force Prince Duan

20:05.830 --> 20:07.760
to let us see His Majesty in person.

20:17.160 --> 20:19.070
My lords, silence please!

20:28.670 --> 20:30.600
Regarding the Mount Bei incident,

20:31.790 --> 20:33.850
His Majesty suffered a severe shock.

20:34.440 --> 20:37.170
His head ailment has flared up,
and he needs rest.

20:37.200 --> 20:38.860
Therefore, the court affairs

20:38.920 --> 20:40.850
will be temporarily handled by me.

20:41.680 --> 20:42.070
This...

20:42.070 --> 20:42.640
This...

20:44.550 --> 20:46.160
In these extraordinary times,

20:46.160 --> 20:48.440
I hope you all will cooperate fully

20:49.000 --> 20:51.260
to help His Majesty through this crisis.

21:02.640 --> 21:03.400
Gentlemen,

21:05.070 --> 21:06.930
do any of you have any objections?

21:38.680 --> 21:41.010
I have something to report, Your Majesty.

21:41.480 --> 21:42.740
Please speak, Lord Wu.

21:42.870 --> 21:43.980
How dare you!

21:47.830 --> 21:48.490
Wu Jiadong,

21:49.310 --> 21:51.160
as a high-ranking official
of the third rank,

21:51.160 --> 21:52.070
with His Majesty absent,

21:52.070 --> 21:54.200
who were you addressing as "Your Majesty"?

21:54.200 --> 21:54.640
No, I...

21:54.640 --> 21:56.440
-This...
-Do you intend to put
His Highness Prince Duan

21:56.440 --> 21:58.240
in a position of treason and rebellion?

21:58.240 --> 21:59.000
This... This is...

21:59.000 --> 21:59.400
You...

22:00.550 --> 22:02.070
I misspoke in the heat of the moment.

22:02.070 --> 22:04.800
Please forgive me,
Your Highness Prince Duan.

22:08.270 --> 22:10.470
Lord Wu simply made a slip of the tongue.

22:11.030 --> 22:12.230
Lord Li, Mr. Li Yunxi,

22:13.240 --> 22:15.240
there's no need for such hostility.

22:16.750 --> 22:17.310
We

22:18.480 --> 22:20.080
live on His Majesty's salary

22:20.550 --> 22:22.280
and serve His Majesty loyally.

22:22.550 --> 22:24.680
If we disregard propriety and the law,

22:24.720 --> 22:27.780
then we're unworthy of
being His Majesty's ministers.

22:27.920 --> 22:30.370
Then how do you intend to act
as a minister?

22:30.510 --> 22:31.200
I

22:32.400 --> 22:35.460
would like to ask
Your Highness Prince Duan a question:

22:36.750 --> 22:37.770
when

22:38.740 --> 22:41.000
can we have an audience with His Majesty?

22:48.510 --> 22:49.760
I've already said it.

22:50.270 --> 22:51.930
His Majesty is critically ill

22:52.720 --> 22:54.270
and needs to rest.

22:54.550 --> 22:56.180
I prefer to see it for myself.

22:56.440 --> 22:57.840
Lord Li, are you implying

22:58.930 --> 23:00.550
that I'm lying?

23:01.240 --> 23:02.640
If there were an imperial decree as proof,

23:02.640 --> 23:03.300
I naturally

23:03.830 --> 23:05.230
would have no objection.

23:07.920 --> 23:10.510
But now, Your Highness Prince Duan
has nothing to show

23:10.510 --> 23:11.550
yet wishes to act as regent.

23:11.550 --> 23:12.250
May I ask—

23:12.960 --> 23:14.230
where is His Majesty,

23:14.270 --> 23:15.680
where is the Crown Prince,

23:15.680 --> 23:18.300
and where is the Empress?

23:29.350 --> 23:31.030
Are you asking me about
that demonic empress?

23:31.030 --> 23:33.330
I also wish to catch that culprit.

23:34.110 --> 23:35.040
However, I heard

23:35.960 --> 23:37.000
that you, Lord Li,

23:37.340 --> 23:39.870
were highly favored by
that demonic empress.

23:39.920 --> 23:41.780
Do you happen to know where she is?

23:42.510 --> 23:43.030
I...

23:43.160 --> 23:43.860
I

23:44.160 --> 23:45.890
observed the stars last night.

23:46.960 --> 23:48.890
The Emperor Star was dim,

23:49.400 --> 23:50.680
and the Treasury Star appeared,

23:50.680 --> 23:52.790
yet it was also shrouded by dark clouds—

23:52.790 --> 23:54.880
much like the current state of affairs,

23:54.880 --> 23:58.210
where things are unclear
as if viewing flowers through fog.

23:59.070 --> 24:01.200
Therefore, what Lord Li meant was that

24:01.440 --> 24:03.350
the Mount Bei incident
is highly suspicious,

24:03.350 --> 24:05.480
with many doubts still unresolved, so

24:05.510 --> 24:08.040
it's far too early
to draw a final conclusion.

24:08.110 --> 24:08.510
But...

24:08.590 --> 24:09.400
But

24:10.750 --> 24:12.400
His Highness Prince Duan would never

24:12.400 --> 24:15.030
base the guilt of the Empress

24:15.110 --> 24:17.540
solely on the word of a mere assassin.

24:17.960 --> 24:18.490
Of course

24:18.510 --> 24:21.240
we'll need to wait for His Majesty
to wake up, right?

24:21.240 --> 24:21.900
Lord Yang.

24:22.240 --> 24:24.110
You are mistaken, Lord Yang.

24:24.590 --> 24:26.550
Lord Li's request to see His Majesty

24:26.550 --> 24:29.400
concerns matters of state
handled by all departments.

24:29.400 --> 24:31.600
What does that have to do with the harem?

24:31.830 --> 24:33.750
Especially for our Ministry of Revenue—

24:33.750 --> 24:35.110
we have no interest

24:35.170 --> 24:36.590
in His Majesty's private affairs.

24:36.590 --> 24:37.400
Am I right,

24:38.350 --> 24:39.390
Lord Chen?

24:45.590 --> 24:48.070
The Ministry of Revenue
has many pressing matters

24:48.070 --> 24:49.200
that indeed require

24:49.510 --> 24:50.680
an audience with His Majesty

24:50.680 --> 24:51.810
as soon as possible.

24:53.240 --> 24:54.140
Exactly.

24:54.510 --> 24:57.640
The Mount Bei incident caused the deaths
and injuries of many court ministers.

24:57.640 --> 25:00.230
Personnel changes cannot be enacted

25:00.550 --> 25:02.830
without His Majesty's seal.

25:03.590 --> 25:05.250
The Empress Dowager's coffin

25:05.270 --> 25:07.000
hasn't been interred, either.

25:07.440 --> 25:09.480
The mausoleum construction
is not yet finished.

25:09.480 --> 25:10.960
I do wish to proceed with the burial,

25:10.960 --> 25:12.190
but how could I?

25:12.880 --> 25:14.340
-That's right.
-Exactly.

25:17.110 --> 25:17.590
Exactly.

25:17.590 --> 25:18.400
Indeed.

25:25.680 --> 25:26.920
Silence!

25:29.340 --> 25:31.600
Once His Majesty has recovered a little,

25:33.890 --> 25:35.690
he'll naturally summon you all.

25:46.750 --> 25:47.830
And when will that be?

25:47.830 --> 25:48.440
When?

25:48.880 --> 25:50.070
Your Highness Prince Duan,

25:50.070 --> 25:51.070
when will that be!

26:02.070 --> 26:05.270
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire
Repeating Sleeve Crossbows.

26:06.180 --> 26:07.240
How many do we have?

26:07.510 --> 26:08.370
Your Highness,

26:08.920 --> 26:10.520
there are thousands of them,

26:10.680 --> 26:12.740
plus dozens of crates of ammunition.

26:18.880 --> 26:19.630
The blueprints

26:19.630 --> 26:21.030
were sent by His Majesty.

26:21.270 --> 26:22.860
To prevent them from being intercepted
along the way,

26:22.860 --> 26:24.680
the crossbows were
dismantled into countless components

26:24.680 --> 26:26.350
and delivered in over 10 shipments.

26:26.350 --> 26:28.410
We then enlisted the best craftsmen,

26:28.480 --> 26:30.080
and after several failures,

26:30.440 --> 26:32.570
we finally put together the first one.

26:33.110 --> 26:34.440
These sleeve crossbows

26:34.920 --> 26:36.270
were extremely difficult to obtain,

26:36.270 --> 26:38.030
but their combat power is unparalleled.

26:38.030 --> 26:38.480
Even

26:39.510 --> 26:42.480
against tens of thousands of troops
of the other two armies,

26:42.480 --> 26:44.240
they'll crush them like dry weeds,

26:44.240 --> 26:46.240
without shedding a drop of our own blood.

26:46.240 --> 26:47.840
Thank you for your hard work.

26:52.790 --> 26:53.330
Today,

26:54.400 --> 26:55.400
our army marches.

26:56.070 --> 26:58.000
At the highlands 500 li from the capital,

26:58.000 --> 26:59.590
we can intercept
the Left and Central Armies.

26:59.590 --> 26:59.880
We

27:00.720 --> 27:02.240
have endured in silence for years,

27:02.240 --> 27:03.570
sleeping on our spears,

27:04.510 --> 27:06.880
just waiting for today—
the moment of certain victory.

27:06.880 --> 27:08.790
Prince Duan conspires in rebellion

27:08.790 --> 27:10.190
and acts as a pawn of evil.

27:11.960 --> 27:13.960
Just give the order, Your Highness,

27:14.200 --> 27:14.800
and we will

27:15.870 --> 27:17.830
execute him for the sake of the realm.

27:17.830 --> 27:19.890
Execute him for the sake of the realm!

27:23.350 --> 27:24.080
General Lin.

27:24.550 --> 27:26.150
Let's have a word in private.

27:30.200 --> 27:31.920
His Majesty's whereabouts
are still unknown.

27:31.920 --> 27:33.050
If we attack rashly,

27:33.550 --> 27:35.550
and he really is in Prince Duan's hands,

27:35.550 --> 27:36.680
what will we do then?

27:37.790 --> 27:39.450
This is the final secret edict

27:39.510 --> 27:41.640
His Majesty gave me before I departed.

27:43.560 --> 27:44.780
[Order Crown Prince to succeed the throne;
confer Yu Wanyin as Empress Dowager]

27:44.800 --> 27:46.480
[Promote Li Yunxi and Yang Duojie
to assist in managing state affairs]

27:46.500 --> 27:47.650
[Traitor Xiahou Bo shall be executed
without hesitation. Put the realm first]

27:46.680 --> 27:48.140
He wants the Crown Prince
to succeed the throne

27:47.680 --> 27:48.740
[at all times; do not concern yourselves
with my life or death]

27:49.720 --> 27:51.310
and me to become the Empress Dowager?

27:51.310 --> 27:52.170
Only in this way

27:52.790 --> 27:55.440
can you justifiably
hold control over the court.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.900
He's also left behind many

27:57.310 --> 27:58.680
to assist in governing state affairs.

27:58.680 --> 28:01.240
Traitor Xiahou Bo shall be executed
without hesitation.

28:01.240 --> 28:03.040
Put the realm first at all times;

28:03.310 --> 28:05.970
do not concern yourselves with
my life or death.

28:06.160 --> 28:06.720
He knew

28:07.510 --> 28:09.170
he didn't have much time left.

28:09.270 --> 28:11.590
He didn't want to become a burden
to you in his final moments,

28:11.590 --> 28:13.920
nor did he wish to be humiliated
in the enemy camp.

28:13.920 --> 28:16.030
If, by misfortune, he were captured
by Prince Duan,

28:16.030 --> 28:18.630
he would find a way to
perish together with him.

28:18.750 --> 28:20.590
And if even that were impossible,

28:20.590 --> 28:21.250
he would...

28:24.070 --> 28:25.000
Take his own life.

28:25.000 --> 28:25.750
So you just

28:25.750 --> 28:27.240
gave up on him as a matter of course?

28:27.240 --> 28:28.040
Of course not!

28:28.750 --> 28:30.400
I've seized every possible chance
to look for him.

28:30.400 --> 28:32.150
Then find him first
before mobilizing the troops!

28:32.150 --> 28:33.920
You know there isn't enough time.

28:33.920 --> 28:36.640
The rebels are marching toward
the capital day and night.

28:36.640 --> 28:38.160
Prince Duan is scouring everywhere
for you,

28:38.160 --> 28:40.360
and he'll soon trace you to my location.

28:40.440 --> 28:42.640
But if Xiahou Dan's safety
cannot be guaranteed,

28:42.640 --> 28:44.190
none of this means anything.

28:44.190 --> 28:45.480
His Majesty's final secret edict

28:45.480 --> 28:46.830
was precisely to force us
to consider the bigger picture

28:46.830 --> 28:48.090
and act without delay.

28:48.200 --> 28:49.000
Lin Xuanying.

28:50.590 --> 28:52.350
Why are you so eager
to mobilize the troops?

28:52.350 --> 28:54.080
What exactly are you planning?

28:56.010 --> 28:57.670
Whether you believe me or not,

28:58.470 --> 29:00.930
I have absolutely no interest in
any of this.

29:01.190 --> 29:02.270
I only came here

29:02.830 --> 29:05.160
on Master's orders to assist His Majesty,

29:05.400 --> 29:07.200
and His Majesty asked me to
take orders from you.

29:07.200 --> 29:07.930
Then my order

29:08.030 --> 29:09.960
is to save him at all costs.

29:12.440 --> 29:12.970
General.

29:16.510 --> 29:17.040
General,

29:17.410 --> 29:19.110
shall we distribute these sleeve crossbows

29:19.110 --> 29:20.000
to the army

29:20.160 --> 29:21.720
and issue orders to prepare for battle?

29:21.720 --> 29:24.380
Deputy General of the Right Army,
Lin Xuanying!

29:29.410 --> 29:29.880
Yes.

29:30.760 --> 29:32.690
His Majesty ordered you to obey me,

29:33.400 --> 29:34.000
didn't he?

29:36.380 --> 29:36.750
Yes.

29:37.010 --> 29:38.520
Then I hereby order you

29:39.700 --> 29:41.360
to discard this secret edict.

29:42.590 --> 29:43.720
From this moment on,

29:45.510 --> 29:46.110
you do

29:47.830 --> 29:48.380
as I say.

30:05.110 --> 30:05.870
My lords.

30:10.270 --> 30:10.800
Lord Li.

30:21.650 --> 30:22.320
My lords,

30:23.400 --> 30:24.730
it is freezing out here.

30:25.110 --> 30:25.510
Please

30:26.310 --> 30:27.530
go back for now.

30:28.160 --> 30:28.880
Eunuch An.

30:30.480 --> 30:31.370
His Majesty

30:32.310 --> 30:33.910
has always treated you well.

30:35.440 --> 30:36.170
Why do you now

30:37.270 --> 30:39.160
only take orders from Prince Duan?

30:39.160 --> 30:40.870
Besides, we are kneeling here

30:41.240 --> 30:42.920
only to pray for His Majesty.

30:44.720 --> 30:46.050
Why is that not allowed?

30:46.680 --> 30:48.200
We will not leave today

30:48.790 --> 30:50.190
until we see His Majesty.

30:52.030 --> 30:52.630
Lord Chen.

30:55.980 --> 30:57.380
That's right, Eunuch An.

30:57.720 --> 30:58.790
Didn't we make it clear

30:58.790 --> 31:00.090
in the court?

31:00.440 --> 31:02.030
The state affairs are complicated

31:02.030 --> 31:03.210
and cannot wait.

31:03.510 --> 31:06.790
We beg to see His Majesty!

31:12.510 --> 31:13.070
My lords,

31:14.350 --> 31:15.610
please heed my advice.

31:17.160 --> 31:18.790
Right now, the last thing
His Majesty wants to see

31:18.790 --> 31:20.750
is a scene like this.

31:21.880 --> 31:23.240
As for the complicated state affairs,

31:23.240 --> 31:24.300
please handle them

31:24.640 --> 31:25.770
yourselves for now.

31:26.510 --> 31:27.970
The situation is chaotic.

31:28.240 --> 31:29.200
It would be better

31:29.200 --> 31:30.260
to observe quietly

31:30.880 --> 31:31.940
before acting.

31:33.270 --> 31:35.350
You're all pillars of Great Xia.

31:37.640 --> 31:38.500
At this moment,

31:39.160 --> 31:41.020
besides head-on confrontation,

31:41.160 --> 31:43.820
what's more important is
to protect yourselves

31:44.310 --> 31:46.310
and proceed with careful planning.

31:46.480 --> 31:47.080
Eunuch An,

31:47.750 --> 31:48.960
there's no need to advise us further.

31:48.960 --> 31:50.820
We don't speak the same language.

31:51.110 --> 31:51.550
We

31:52.350 --> 31:53.210
will not leave.

31:55.350 --> 31:55.960
Eunuch An!

31:56.690 --> 31:57.290
Eunuch An!

31:58.590 --> 31:59.120
Bad news!

31:59.480 --> 32:00.010
Bad news!

32:00.480 --> 32:01.740
His... His Majesty...

32:04.590 --> 32:05.450
His Majesty...

32:06.550 --> 32:09.970
His Majesty has passed away!

32:10.640 --> 32:12.510
Your Majesty.

32:17.550 --> 32:19.640
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

32:22.000 --> 32:22.800
Your Majesty.

32:26.400 --> 32:27.830
Your Majesty!

32:33.920 --> 32:35.920
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

32:36.800 --> 32:39.730
I'll take good care of
the young Crown Prince for you.

32:42.240 --> 32:43.640
In these troubled times,

32:45.310 --> 32:47.570
our state cannot go a day without a ruler.

32:48.000 --> 32:52.200
Let's prepare for the Crown Prince's
enthronement ceremony immediately.

32:53.640 --> 32:54.680
Where are the Yulin Guards?

32:54.680 --> 32:55.210
Present!

32:57.510 --> 33:00.640
Escort the lords back to their residences
to rest for now

33:00.680 --> 33:01.880
and prepare to
observe the mourning period.

33:01.880 --> 33:02.160
Yes!

33:06.640 --> 33:07.480
Report!

33:10.030 --> 33:10.560
General,

33:10.880 --> 33:11.790
urgent news from the capital!

33:11.790 --> 33:13.200
His Majesty has passed away!

33:13.200 --> 33:13.990
Nonsense!

33:17.480 --> 33:18.810
Go and verify this news.

33:19.160 --> 33:19.560
Go now!

33:19.750 --> 33:20.030
Yes!

33:24.440 --> 33:25.570
Continue the march!

33:33.160 --> 33:34.020
Your Highness,

33:34.440 --> 33:35.570
you heard it, right?

33:35.680 --> 33:36.680
That's good news.

33:37.160 --> 33:38.020
Your Highness?

33:39.750 --> 33:41.920
If Prince Duan had really captured
His Majesty,

33:41.920 --> 33:43.250
given his personality,

33:43.960 --> 33:46.240
there's no way
he would have let His Majesty die.

33:46.240 --> 33:49.110
After all, only a living hostage
is a bargaining chip.

33:49.110 --> 33:50.170
As for His Majesty,

33:50.550 --> 33:52.150
no matter what he said to you,

33:52.590 --> 33:54.160
before confirming my safety,

33:54.160 --> 33:55.920
he would never take his own life.

33:55.920 --> 33:58.160
So this news of his death actually proves

33:58.160 --> 34:00.760
that His Majesty is not
in Prince Duan's hands.

34:01.070 --> 34:02.030
It must be so.

34:02.890 --> 34:03.710
Could it be

34:05.110 --> 34:06.350
because of His Majesty's illness...

34:06.350 --> 34:06.860
No.

34:08.190 --> 34:10.250
He said he would never leave me alone.

34:11.320 --> 34:13.550
He absolutely wouldn't break his promise.

34:13.550 --> 34:14.000
Your Highness.

34:14.000 --> 34:14.659
Say no more.

34:15.710 --> 34:17.630
Prince Duan is a master at
manipulating public opinion.

34:17.630 --> 34:18.489
I won't believe

34:18.960 --> 34:20.159
a single word he says.

34:35.310 --> 34:36.960
We'll be encamping here tonight.

34:36.960 --> 34:37.760
The conditions are rough.

34:37.760 --> 34:38.110
Your Highness, you...

34:38.110 --> 34:39.030
Don't worry about me.

34:39.030 --> 34:39.920
Focus on

34:40.360 --> 34:41.889
finding His Majesty first.

34:51.480 --> 34:52.940
Didn't I tell you to leave?

34:53.110 --> 34:54.770
How come you followed me here?

35:27.360 --> 35:28.960
But I can't let you tag along.

35:37.530 --> 35:39.730
It's not that I can't afford to feed you,

35:39.760 --> 35:40.940
but we are going to war.

35:40.940 --> 35:42.140
It's very dangerous.

35:42.550 --> 35:43.960
You could lose your life.

36:02.190 --> 36:03.710
But you are too young.

36:05.480 --> 36:07.210
I can't use child labor, right?

36:28.840 --> 36:29.840
Are you telling me

36:32.280 --> 36:33.210
not to be afraid?

36:50.440 --> 36:50.880
I know.

36:54.230 --> 36:55.110
I'm not afraid.

36:59.590 --> 37:01.050
I'll definitely find him.

37:57.440 --> 37:58.140
Don't go outside.

37:58.140 --> 37:58.920
Wait for me here.
